text: I remember ( is the fifth studio album by Ukrainian singer Tina Karol. The album cover is designed in the form of a painting: the singer is depicted on the cover both closed and defenseless at the same time. Along with the CD, the album includes a booklet in the form of a diary, all the lyrics are written in verse form on sheets of paper from a squared notebook. The last page of the diary contains a few lines from the singer herself. == References ==
title: I remember
